author: Howard Kurtz
title: Virus vertigo spins the news, pushing out almost everything else
description: These days we all spend most of our time talking, writing, thinking and worrying about the coronavirus
content:
The Michelle Obama non-story is a perfect example of things we used to care about.
It’s a BS piece of clickbait, to be sure. The former first lady has insisted she will never run for office, but Politico and others ran pieces on how Democrats are fantasizing… [+5827 chars]
